Rule: Changing the gender from Female to Male has a significant positive impact on the outcome.
Increasing the education level from Bachelors to Masters can lead to a positive outcome.
Changing marital status from Divorced to Married can lead to a positive outcome.
Increasing the number of hours worked per week can lead to a positive outcome.
Staying in the same occupation (Service) but changing the workclass to Self-Employed can lead to a positive outcome.
The combination of being Male, working in the Government sector, and having a constant education level (Bachelors) leads to a positive outcome.
